{"tid":1672203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北京又爆非法拆遷 3000戶「中端人口」受害、損失百億！","createTime":"2019-10-24T03:25:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T10:16:15.000Z","uid":105678,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"43c2f9e536163120925e7fd59935dc1e361a3f75","tid":1672203,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:25:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AwZkdC0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAwZkdC0.jpg&h=51e8b327&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">中國強拆事件層出不窮，常引爆官民激烈衝突，此為示意圖，與本新聞無關。（擷取自大中華在線）</span><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國北京市昌平區近日爆發非法拆遷爭議，數千家庭控訴，其合法購入的房舍竟被政府誣指為「違章建築」，甚至將其驅離出境，合計損失金額高達數十億人民幣（約合新台幣上百億元）。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國《自由亞洲電台》報導，昌平區崔村鎮香堂文化新村3000多名業主上週五（18日）圍堵當地政府，抗議當局將該村村民此前購入的房屋認定違章建築，勒令近期拆遷並拒絕補償的措施。<br />\n<br />\n現場受害者出示20年前由當局核發，包含村、鄉、區三級政府及國土局蓋章的協議，證明其房舍在購入時獲得國家批准一切合法，痛批鄉政府「說推翻就推翻，只給受害者3天時間，接下來就動工強拆，讓我們露宿街頭」。<br />\n<br />\n受害者不滿表示，當局舉出許多法規，欲證明拆遷戶確實是違建，但這些法案都在住戶買房後才推出，「全都是我們買了房、住了家，你們國土局蓋章後的事，今日政府後法管前事，根本沒道理」。<br />\n<br />\n還有業主激動地表示，拆遷以後政府沒有提供絲毫安置及賠償方案，「所以大家都寫了遺囑、立了生死書，就是要跟他們（指政府）拚了」。"},{"pid":"5db9b1785143486f5ed218b313738d07d68210f4","tid":1672203,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:26:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>警</strong>犯咗死罪</span>，已<span style=\"color: red;\">大禍臨頭</span>！<br />\n+ <span style=\"color: gold;\">送條妙計<strong>俾科士</strong>解圍</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1671833\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1671833</a>"},{"pid":"57f695cae4762235140309933f555d24fb8494e2","tid":1672203,"uid":60434,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:26:47.000Z","msg":"寫了遺囑、立了生死書<br />\n<br />\n一定用得著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />RIP"},{"pid":"08433368810efba238d50a78f2640c0a29ce2ed6","tid":1672203,"uid":176282,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:27:36.000Z","msg":"算好喇，低端人口一早變咗豬肉"},{"pid":"c9405011a43519f35738a01d2661764b8cd0a3b8","tid":1672203,"uid":28812,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:29:12.000Z","msg":"法律就係法律 ，<br />\n譴責北京暴徒破壞法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf9a1863d22eddcb5c89c07ad7c7a6677c468dfa","tid":1672203,"uid":183834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wyWVM0g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwyWVM0g.jpg&h=a0ce9ab5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2015867276c134329bb10c774ce90a83e9226bdd","tid":1672203,"uid":275692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:34:14.000Z","msg":"支持止暴制亂"},{"pid":"a646e648913539b8531b0bb686eff0ff22e7f604","tid":1672203,"uid":118973,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:34:54.000Z","msg":"裡面唔知有幾多半個月前仲係護旗手呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c830d883dbac1aeb412d27876e1661441aa24d56","tid":1672203,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:35:56.000Z","msg":"點拼<br />\nwe7俾錢都知你係邊啦"},{"pid":"49022fcdd3f077c74c1353fb753b03e3065b265e","tid":1672203,"uid":41545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:40:13.000Z","msg":"班廢老又出黎搞搞震<br />\n國家要穩定 有國才有家 懂不<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72791da8eff195bf0de0ea662349679506fbd9e6","tid":1672203,"uid":213747,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:41:35.000Z","msg":"聽講五毛優先拆 因為佢成個群體都係五毛唔會幫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa1c3fd179af23bbcc68b4dabc0ff1cd8781b988","tid":1672203,"uid":31720